Class StartTimes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ning.billing.meter.timeline.shutdown.StartTimes

  • public class StartTimes
extends Object
    This class is used solely as a Json mapping class when saving timelines in a database blob on shutdown, and restoring them on startup.

    The Map> maps from sourceId to eventCategoryId to startTime.
